  "datePublished": "2026-04-27",
  "description": "The formation in which California — the actual coastal territory and the imaginative screen — has served as the historical laboratory in which the apparatus iterates: a continuous test-and-export of subject-formatting infrastructures, from the Misiones Californianas through the Gold Rush, Hollywood, Esalen, Silicon Valley, and the wellness industry, each phase a stage of one apparatus rather than separate phenomena.",
  "name": "Californian projection",
